				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">This kinda exists today... except it's still triangles all the way down.<br /><br />You send a small amount of data to the GPU (e.g. 6 vertices), and then the GPU can generate all the triangles it wants from it. Doing things this way can be a good optimization because memory transfers are slow.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

