						<div class="postbody">Oh yeah, I also forgot to mention &quot;<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Parallax_mapping" class="postlink">parallax mapping</a>&quot;, which is like putting a heightfield in a texture and having a mini-raytracer in the shader.<br /><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6B-5a2HWqpw" class="postlink">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6B-5a2HWqpw</a><br /><br />Sort of taking the normal map idea to a further extreme.</div>

